               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380618-name-589" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-589" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-589" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-589" type="given" value="EMILY"></interp>EMILY JONES</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a milliner's shop in Wilstead-street, Somers Town. At half-past seven o'clock on the evening of the 24th of May, I was serving a customer in the shop, and Jane Wyatt called out—I went out and saw her in the passage with the prisoner—he had this gown and box—he dropped them as soon as I went into the passage—the box contains the articles stated.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
