                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-590" type="given" value="JANE"></interp>JANE WYATT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Miss Jones's. I saw the prisoner take the gown down—I did not see him take the box, but he had it—I called out and seized him, and he dropped the things—there was another boy who ran away.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
